This paper is about the word2vec model, which is a popular technique in natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which covers topics related to NLP and computational linguistics. The paper also discusses neural networks and optimization techniques, which are covered in categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper is relevant to the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR), as word embeddings are used in various applications in these fields.
